.TH "virtio_dma_buf_export" 9 "virtio_dma_buf_export" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
virtio_dma_buf_export \- Creates a new dma-buf for a virtio exported object
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "struct dma_buf *" virtio_dma_buf_export
.BI "(const struct dma_buf_export_info *exp_info "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "exp_info" 12
[in] see \fBdma_buf_export\fP. ops MUST refer to a dma_buf_ops
struct embedded in a virtio_dma_buf_ops.
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
This wraps \fBdma_buf_export\fP to allow virtio drivers to create a dma-buf
for an virtio exported object that can be queried by other virtio drivers
for the object's UUID.
